me.Abhigya.core.util.configurable.itemstack

Class ConfigurableItemStack

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.Abhigya.core.util.configurable.itemstack.ConfigurableItemStack
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Configurable, Loadable, Saveable, Validable

    public class ConfigurableItemStack
extends java.lang.Object
implements Configurable
    Represents a ItemStack that is 'Configurable' because can be loaded from/saved on a ConfigurationSection.
